asset.hookText:
The queen's stage from Innsbruck to Bolzano over the mountain pass Jaufen: 161km through extreme weathers! E-biker Marcel Schwager is fighting simultaneously against cold, rain & empty batteries and hurling into daring manoeuver.
Happiness on the top: the rally teams are jolly glad to cross the mountain pass Jaufen. It is the highest point of the e-miglia 2010 and from here on it is a downhill where the recuperation technique ist becoming important.
